    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been meticulously preserved with no visible signs of wear or tear. Mechanically, it is in perfect order, having received regular maintenance and careful handling throughout its life. Buyers can expect a like-new driving experience and a vehicle that requires zero immediate investment or repairs.",
      "price": 49500.0,
